text: <@U02F8LF2X> and I have been hearing a cat mewing all morning outside. So we went outside to investigate. It turns out that the antique place across the street has a speaker box outside that is playing jungle noises loudly into the air. I'm surprisingly annoyed by this because I was genuinely concerned that there was a scared kitten somewhere, and that i'd have to figure out wtf to do about it if we found it.
